## Spacing System

### Base Unit: 4px

The design uses an 4px/8px base spacing system.

### Spacing Scale

| Token | Value | Usage |
|-------|-------|-------|
| `space.1` | 4px | Minimal gaps |
| `space.2` | 8px | Small gaps, icon spacing |
| `space.3` | 12px | Form gaps, compact spacing |
| `space.4` | 16px | Standard gaps, card padding |
| `space.5` | 20px | Medium gaps, section spacing |
| `space.6` | 24px | Large gaps |
| `space.7` | 28px | Extra large gaps |
| `space.8` | 32px | Section spacing |
| `space.10` | 40px | Large section gaps |
| `space.12` | 48px | Major section spacing |
| `space.16` | 64px | Huge spacing |
| `space.20` | 80px | Section padding |

### Component-Specific Spacing

#### Cards
- **Padding**: `16px` (standard), `20px` (benefits), `24px` (overlays)
- **Gap between cards**: `20px` (grid), `40px` (hero gallery)
- **Internal gaps**: `7px-12px` (title to description)

#### Forms
- **Field gap**: `36px` (horizontal), `16px` (vertical)
- **Label to input**: `12px`
- **Input padding**: `16px`
- **Submit button top margin**: `48px`

#### Sections
- **Section top/bottom padding**: `78px` (desktop)
- **Container horizontal padding**: `83-84px`
- **Section internal gap**: `24px-32px`

