## Performance Guidelines

### Image Optimization

#### Format Recommendations
- **Photos**: WebP (with JPEG fallback)
- **Illustrations**: SVG (when possible)
- **Icons**: SVG sprite sheet

#### Size Guidelines
- Hero images: Max 1920px width, 75% quality
- Card images: Max 800px width, 80% quality
- Thumbnails: Max 400px width, 85% quality

#### Implementation
```html
<picture>
  <source srcset="hero.webp" type="image/webp">
  <source srcset="hero.jpg" type="image/jpeg">
  <img src="hero.jpg" alt="..." loading="lazy" decoding="async">
</picture>
```

### Lazy Loading

```html
<!-- Images below the fold -->
<img src="..." alt="..." loading="lazy">

<!-- Intersection Observer for complex components -->
<script>
  const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
    entries.forEach(entry => {
      if (entry.isIntersecting) {
        // Load component
        observer.unobserve(entry.target);
      }
    });
  });
</script>
```

### CSS Optimization

1. **Critical CSS**: Inline above-the-fold styles
2. **Minification**: Remove whitespace and comments
3. **Purge unused CSS**: Use PurgeCSS or similar
4. **Avoid @import**: Use link tags instead

### JavaScript Optimization

1. **Code Splitting**: Split by route/section
2. **Tree Shaking**: Remove unused code
3. **Defer non-critical JS**: Use `defer` attribute
4. **Minimize DOM manipulation**: Batch updates

### Performance Targets

| Metric | Target | Tool |
|--------|--------|------|
| First Contentful Paint (FCP) | < 1.8s | Lighthouse |
| Largest Contentful Paint (LCP) | < 2.5s | Lighthouse |
| Time to Interactive (TTI) | < 3.8s | Lighthouse |
| Cumulative Layout Shift (CLS) | < 0.1 | Lighthouse |
| Total Blocking Time (TBT) | < 200ms | Lighthouse |
| Page Weight | < 2MB | DevTools |

